Title: Getaway
DateModified: '2018-02-23'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/getaway
SetInCountry: Usa
Category: A decision that pushed me to the edge
AuthorName: Elvia Guerra
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: I need to get away from my boyfriend. I feel like we have reached a point in
  our relationship that we need to go or separate ways. I really regret to have wasted
  my time with him. I wish him the best but we need to go our separate ways. My travel
  story will be get out, get away! Enjoy the world enjoy life cause travel is the
  spice to life!
